---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
	title="Contact Us"
	description="Get in touch with the City Walks team"
>
<div class="content">
	<h2>Get in Touch</h2>
	<p>
		We'd love to hear from you! Whether you have questions about a specific walk, 
		suggestions for new routes, or want to contribute your own city expertise, 
		we're here to help.
	</p>

	<div class="contact-methods">
		<div class="contact-method">
			<h3>üìß Email Us</h3>
			<p>For general inquiries, route suggestions, or partnership opportunities:</p>
			<p><strong>hello@citywalks.com</strong></p>
		</div>

		<div class="contact-method">
			<h3>üó∫Ô∏è Suggest a Route</h3>
			<p>Know a great walking route that should be featured? Share it with us!</p>
			<p><strong>routes@citywalks.com</strong></p>
		</div>

		<div class="contact-method">
			<h3>ü§ù Partnerships</h3>
			<p>Tourism boards, local guides, and walking organizations - let's collaborate!</p>
			<p><strong>partners@citywalks.com</strong></p>
		</div>

		<div class="contact-method">
			<h3>üêõ Report Issues</h3>
			<p>Found outdated information or technical problems? Help us improve!</p>
			<p><strong>support@citywalks.com</strong></p>
		</div>
	</div>

	<h2>Contribute a Walk</h2>
	<p>
		Are you a local expert, tour guide, or passionate walker? We're always looking for 
		authentic routes curated by people who know their cities best. Here's what we look for:
	</p>
	
	<ul>
		<li><strong>Local Knowledge:</strong> Routes that showcase both famous spots and hidden gems</li>
		<li><strong>Clear Navigation:</strong> Easy-to-follow paths with clear start and end points</li>
		<li><strong>Cultural Context:</strong> Stories and historical background that bring places to life</li>
		<li><strong>Practical Information:</strong> Realistic timing, difficulty levels, and useful tips</li>
		<li><strong>Safety Considerations:</strong> Routes that are safe and accessible for most walkers</li>
	</ul>

	<h2>Response Times</h2>
	<p>
		We typically respond to all inquiries within 2-3 business days. For urgent matters 
		or time-sensitive suggestions, please mention this in your subject line.
	</p>

	<div class="social-section">
		<h2>Follow Our Journey</h2>
		<p>Stay updated with new routes, walking tips, and community stories:</p>
		<div class="social-links">
			<a href="#" class="social-link">Instagram</a>
			<a href="#" class="social-link">Twitter</a>
			<a href="#" class="social-link">Facebook</a>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
	.content {
		max-width: 1000px;
		margin: 2rem auto;
		padding: 0 2rem;
	}
	.contact-methods {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
		margin: 3rem 0;
	}

	.contact-method {
		padding: 2rem;
		background: #f8f9fa;
		border-radius: 8px;
		border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
	}

	.contact-method h3 {
		margin-top: 0;
		color: #333;
	}

	.contact-method p {
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.social-section {
		margin-top: 3rem;
		padding: 2rem;
		background: #f8f9fa;
		border-radius: 8px;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.social-links {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
		gap: 1rem;
		margin-top: 1rem;
	}

	.social-link {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
		background: #667eea;
		color: white;
		text-decoration: none;
		border-radius: 4px;
		transition: background 0.2s;
	}

	.social-link:hover {
		background: #764ba2;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.contact-methods {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
		
		.social-links {
			flex-direction: column;
			align-items: center;
		}
	}
</style>